{"tid":2317612,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門變態燒鳩未死 要人","createTime":"2020-12-08T17:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T12:12:08.000Z","uid":286788,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92c8f927ecfbedf27f94155dd22479181454153b","tid":2317612,"uid":286788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"請救鳩!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n之前個變態男仔燒鴿/鳩眼單案，可以再推推個post <br />\n, 我深信警察唔會幫手揾雀，大家唔好放棄搵返隻受傷嘅鴿/ 鳩B出嚟，<br />\n佢燒傷面眼不至死，佢好大機會失救失温餓死！<br />\n<br />\n我懇請屯門友及大興邨附近嘅人幫忙望吓....過咗今晚佢生存嘅機會率就會更低！<br />\n<br />\n鳩b未死，要好好救牠，死咗亦要好好安葬，我地對唔住佢。佢要做證據，好好防止千萬個變態佬!<br />\n<br />\n牠可能在屯門河邊，草叢附近，大興村<br />\n<br />\n各位義工，搵動物，餵動物，餵浪浪，遇到他，請hold可憐鳩鳩，已有義工搵牠，但仲未搵到。<br />\n<br />\n如拾獲，請hold，保暖，請回post，各大雀鳥義工即到救<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/130429893638715/posts/4026123677402631/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F130429893638715%2Fposts%2F4026123677402631%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=b1a11f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/130429893638715/posts/4026123677402631/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1434b0114020cae5a7bd79f5f1819af295714ea8","tid":2317612,"uid":286788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2fe79c396bb823e2fe3498895699c92c8266d4","tid":2317612,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3464639cfe18676f4f2ac372ac85930f019